sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User/CI Pipeline
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>Go Operator
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP TCP<br/>Optional TLS
    participant Kubelet as kubelet<br/>Pod Scheduler
    participant Puller as Runtime Puller<br/>in Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>Java Service
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.3
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP<br/>Optional TLS
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant MLServer as ML Framework<br/>(Triton/MLServer/<br/>OpenVINO/TorchServe)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,ModelMesh: Flow 1: Model Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event
        Controller->>etcd: Register model metadata<br/>Optional mTLS
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Kubelet: Schedule pods
        Kubelet->>Puller: Start runtime pod
        Puller->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS Signature V4
        S3-->>Puller: Model files
        Puller->>Adapter: Load model
        Adapter->>ModelMesh: Register model<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Update model status<br/>Optional TLS
        ModelMesh-->>Controller: Model ready
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor status
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Client,MLServer: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST gRPC inference request<br/>Auth: Optional Bearer Token
        Gateway->>ModelMesh: Forward gRPC<br/>8033/TCP Optional mTLS
        ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to model<br/>UDS/8080 gRPC
        Adapter->>MLServer: Framework-specific call<br/>UDS/runtime-specific
        MLServer-->>Adapter: Prediction result
        Adapter-->>ModelMesh: gRPC response
        ModelMesh-->>Gateway: gRPC response
        Gateway-->>Client: Inference result
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,MLServer: Flow 3: REST Inference Request
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/model-name/infer<br/>Auth: Optional Bearer Token
        Gateway->>RESTProxy: Forward HTTP<br/>8008/TCP Optional TLS
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Convert to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP Optional mTLS
        ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to model<br/>UDS/8080 gRPC
        Adapter->>MLServer: Framework call<br/>UDS/runtime-specific
        MLServer-->>Adapter: Prediction
        Adapter-->>ModelMesh: gRPC response
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>Gateway: JSON response
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
        Note over Prometheus,ModelMesh: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: OAuth
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
        Prometheus->>ModelMesh: GET /metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP
        ModelMesh-->>Prometheus: Runtime metrics
    end
